# VERSIONING.gal

## Purpose
Defines the versioning strategy for the Galaxy Node Pool and Node components, following the Gelato Protocol standard.

## Versioning Strategy
- Semantic Versioning (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)
- MAJOR: Breaking changes to API or protocol
- MINOR: New features, backward compatible
- PATCH: Bug fixes, backward compatible

## Current Versions
- Galaxy Node Pool: 0.1.0 (Beta)
- Galaxy Node: 0.1.0 (Beta)
- Protocol: 1.0.0

## Version History
- 0.1.0 (2025-05-28): Initial beta release
  - Modular architecture
  - Plugin system
  - Public/private pool support
  - Main net federation

## Release Cycle
- Beta releases: Monthly
- Stable releases: Quarterly
- LTS releases: Yearly

